---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-section-padding-desktop hero-mask bg-primary overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
<div class="absolute inset-0 islamic-pattern"></div>
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale animate-float" data-alt="A cinematic, low-angle shot of a grand educational building featuring elegant stone arches and large wooden doors, captured during the golden hour with soft, warm sunlight illuminating the textures. The scene exudes a sense of prestige, tradition, and intellectual serenity, following a muted olive and warm cream color palette with high-contrast shadows." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBKSGCwbDKWV5T340nZqRLubP3QU-Pwwqrut26Z0MhwDtRwFSVTnZrHfQQ5VZGQ5rrbzNJ4EE7admwI_OMGbkOH93Gte3bHdhGJWkMgi2AeLuvocwkabRB6BtRRw25Mad16xPcWVjip0e6ycxc_AMdqsWOLJHI7OJtAjE5nVl6RzWJojqQ7v5ZNojrvqzuTZmqTt-I0xDryESML9NptsQfO4fTuhH8NSDec2kze0wRSYy7a7kkDBvD8d0avAE1OM_bqupfDhhFp6ko">
</div>
<div class="relative container mx-auto px-gutter text-center max-w-4xl">
<h1 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg text-on-primary mb-6">Profil Sekolah</h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-primary/90 leading-relaxed">
                Membangun Generasi Rabbani melalui pendidikan yang berlandaskan Al-Qur'an dan As-Sunnah, memadukan tradisi keilmuan Islam dengan inovasi laboratorium pendidikan modern.
            </p>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Tentang Kami Section -->
<section class="py-section-padding-desktop container mx-auto px-gutter">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center reveal active">
<div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
<div class="relative">
<div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 bg-tertiary-fixed opacity-30 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<img class="rounded-lg shadow-xl w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover animate-float" data-alt="A clean, minimalist composition of classical leather-bound books and wooden calligraphy tools arranged neatly on a polished oak table. The lighting is bright and natural, coming from a nearby window, creating a serene and scholarly atmosphere consistent with a modern laboratory school aesthetic. The colors emphasize deep olive and warm wood tones." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDb4gslUDSa6qouCpJkJj2IfYJXr_gZF3jSC73lDJhW7w-c0CJSpjSq84zeHapJrgb7VnFVBLi_A-iAuWQa1dKsPcz3oIKt6Ne2dMbUaW0APtknL9YR79lyIxYv5HkdQ3vvPTQ9aVNKWYJjPFg81A2yYwUjoZ_cINbSJfGa2PDof_fr-Wl16cnkPwLooy30R4EPUqRXKpbQvWIeTN8ibsRuucJ6P6zrgMnFSmsV9QyZD3-9_I2e_uHR7XZQ2VNCdameRr53FhnVXtIDTw">
</div>
</div>
<div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
<span class="font-label-caps text-label-caps text-secondary mb-4 block">TENTANG KAMI</span>
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary mb-6">Menempa Fitrah, Mengukir Prestasi</h2>
<div class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant font-body-md text-body-md">
<p class="">Tarbiyah Sunnah Islamic Lab School hadir sebagai institusi pendidikan model yang mengedepankan pembinaan aqidah dan akhlak dalam rangka membangun generasi rabbani. Sebagai "Lab School", kami senantiasa mengembangkan metode pembelajaran yang relevan dengan perkembangan anak namun tetap teguh pada prinsip syar'i.</p>
<p class="">Kami melayani jenjang <strong>Preschool (PAUD)</strong> dan <strong>Elementary (SD)</strong>, menciptakan lingkungan belajar yang tenang, natural, dan suportif bagi pertumbuhan fitrah setiap anak didik.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section><section class="py-section-padding-desktop bg-surface-container-low reveal active">
<div class="container mx-auto px-gutter">
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary text-center mb-12">Perjalanan Kami</h2>
<div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto border-l-2 border-primary/20 pl-8 ml-4 space-y-12 active" id="timeline-container">
<div class="absolute left-[-2px] top-0 w-[2px] bg-primary timeline-line active" id="timeline-progress"></div>
<div class="relative timeline-item">
<div class="absolute -left-[41px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-primary rounded-full timeline-dot active"></div>
<span class="font-label-caps text-secondary">2021</span>
<h4 class="font-headline-sm text-primary mt-2">Terselenggaranya program preschool online</h4>
</div>
<div class="relative timeline-item">
<div class="absolute -left-[41px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-primary rounded-full timeline-dot active"></div>
<span class="font-label-caps text-secondary">2023</span>
<h4 class="font-headline-sm text-primary mt-2">Berdiri preschool offline</h4>
</div>
<div class="relative timeline-item">
<div class="absolute -left-[41px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-primary rounded-full timeline-dot active"></div>
<span class="font-label-caps text-secondary">2024</span>
<h4 class="font-headline-sm text-primary mt-2">Elementary school</h4>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Visi & Misi Section -->
<section class="py-section-padding-desktop bg-surface-container-low relative reveal active">
<div class="container mx-auto px-gutter">
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-gutter">
<div class="bg-white p-12 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/30 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary">visibility</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-primary">Visi Kami</h3>
</div>
<p class="font-accent-arabic text-primary italic text-2xl leading-relaxed mb-6">"Membangun Generasi Berkarakter Rabbani, Beradab, dan Berilmu."</p>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body-md">Visi ini menjadi kompas utama kami dalam setiap kurikulum and aktivitas, memastikan anak tidak hanya cerdas secara intelektual, namun kokoh dalam ketauhidan.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-primary p-12 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-on-primary hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary-fixed">assignment</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm">Misi Sekolah</h3>
</div>
<ul class="space-y-6">
<li class="flex gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary-fixed">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-body-md">Menginternalisasi nilai-nilai Al-Qur'an dan As-Sunnah sesuai pemahaman Salafush Shalih dalam kehidupan sehari-hari.</span>
</li>
<li class="flex gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary-fixed">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-body-md">Menyelenggarakan pendidikan ramah anak yang menghargai keunikan dan tahapan perkembangan individu.</span>
</li>
<li class="flex gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary-fixed">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-body-md">Mengembangkan kompetensi akademik dan keterampilan hidup (life skills) yang adaptif terhadap tantangan zaman.</span>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section><section class="py-section-padding-desktop container mx-auto px-gutter reveal active">
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary text-center mb-12">Struktur &amp; Kepemimpinan</h2>
