<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl">corporate_fare</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-headline-sm text-primary">Ketua Yayasan</h4>
<p class="font-label-caps text-secondary mt-1">Asep Dadang Sukarna Hikmat Nirwana</p>
</div>
<div class="text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/20 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
<div class="w-24 h-24 bg-surface-container mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl">workspace_premium</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-headline-sm text-primary">Ketua Bidang Pendidikan Yayasan</h4>
<p class="font-label-caps text-secondary mt-1">Mochammad Hilman Al-Fiqhy, M.A.</p>
</div>
<div class="text-center p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/20 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
<div class="w-24 h-24 bg-surface-container mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl">school</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-headline-sm text-primary">PLT Kepala Unit TS Islamic Lab School</h4>
<p class="font-label-caps text-secondary mt-1">Yahya Nursidik, S.Pd, M.T</p>
