<p class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Menitikberatkan pada pembentukan akhlak mulia dan etika islami sejak dini.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-[0px_4px_20px_rgba(63,78,47,0.08)] border border-outline-variant/20 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-surface-container rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">architecture</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-primary mb-3">Akademik Terarah</h4>
<p class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Kurikulum yang terintegrasi, logis, dan merangsang daya kritis siswa.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-[0px_4px_20px_rgba(63,78,47,0.08)] border border-outline-variant/20 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-surface-container rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">eco</span>
</div>
